---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Sponsor docs"
  description="Run the sponsor Docker image and understand the additional deployment options."
>
  <Section
    eyebrow="sponsor"
    title="Deploy the sponsor edition with Docker"
    lede="Sponsors get a Docker-first distribution with the richer standalone package, support levels, and fully offline deployment options."
  >
    <ol>
      <li>Pull the sponsor image from the container registry.</li>
      <li>Run it directly with Docker for a local or production endpoint.</li>
      <li>Choose the support tier that matches your deployment size and operational needs.</li>
    </ol>
    <pre><code>docker run --rm -p 8000:8000 ghcr.io/thumbrella/thumbrella-sponsor:latest serve</code></pre>
    <p>
      Sponsor deployments stay suitable for disconnected environments while adding packaged runtime
      conveniences, advanced operational features, and access to support for teams that need a more
      complete standalone offering.
    </p>
  </Section>
</MainLayout>